$ heketi-cli cluster info 886a86a868711bef83001
.fi
.RE
.RE
.PP
\fBheketi\-cli cluster list\fP
.RS
Lists the clusters managed by Heketi
.PP
\fBExample\fP
.RS
.nf
$ heketi-cli cluster list
.fi
.RE
